			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_64409128"></span>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64409128"><p>I use Cygwin under my Windows notebook from work and my workstation at home. It works pretty well.</p><p>I tried WSL when it first came out but it is a per-user install so I don't use it. I wonder if running iPerf3 under WSL is better than using a version compiled with Cygwin libraries.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64409128">

</div>
</div>

